    <item>
      <title>由于金属价格暴跌，Sibanye 遭受 25 亿美元减值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/sibanye-takes-2-5-billion-impairment-after-metal-prices-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sibanye Stillwater Ltd.预计去年将出现亏损，原因是铂族金属价格暴跌以及其各业务的运营问题迫使其计提了 475 亿兰特（25 亿美元）的减值准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/sibanye-takes-2-5-billion-impairment-after-metal-prices-slump</guid>
